c: 9
v: 31
t: "Kinowa iran so manga Olama kiran go so manga Barasimba kiran a manga Katohanan a salakao ko Allah, go so Al-Masih a Wata o Maryam; a da-a ini Sogo Kiran a rowar ko Kasimba-a Iran ko (Allah a) Tohan a Isa Isa: Da-a Tohan a inonta Sukaniyan. Soti Sukaniyan: Mawatan ko Ipushakoto iran non"